OL,6,FA man has been jailed for life with a
OL,7,Fminimum term of 10 years for killing
OL,8,Fhis disabled wife of 56 years.
OL,10,FPeter Matthews, 80, killed his wife
OL,11,FCarol, 73, who was paraplegic, at
OL,12,Ftheir home in Denton Grove, Weston
OL,13,FCoyney, Stoke-on-Trent, in March.
OL,15,FStafford Crown Court heard that Mrs
OL,16,FMatthews pleaded with her husband not
OL,17,Fto kill her and tried to fight him off
OL,18,Fas he smothered her.
