OL,6,FMatthews called 999 and admitted he
OL,7,Fhad killed his wife to "put her out of
OL,8,Fher misery" even though she did not
OL,9,Fwant to die. He spent two days after
OL,10,Fkilling her trying to take his own
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,F'I decided we had had enough'
OL,15,FProsecutor David Mason KC told the
OL,16,Fcourt Carol Matthews was "fiercely
OL,17,Findependent" and an "extrovert", while
OL,18,Fher husband was "quiet" but was
OL,19,F"loving and caring, doting on his
OL,20,Fwife".
