OL,6,F"Carol was extremely vulnerable due to
OL,7,Fher age and her disability. This
OL,8,Fwasn't just putting a pillow over her
OL,9,Fhead while she was asleep, she was
OL,10,Fawake and knew what he was doing.
OL,12,FIt must be seen that he was full and
OL,13,Ffrank with his admissions from the
OL,14,Fstart including that Carol told him to
OL,15,Fstop but he carried on regardless."
OL,17,F'He was and remains tired of life'
