OL,6,FDefending Matthews, Anis Ali said the
OL,7,Fmurder was the "culmination of many
OL,8,Fyears of emotional and physical
OL,9,Ffragility experienced by Peter and
OL,10,FCarol".
OL,12,FHe said: "They enjoyed together many
OL,13,Fdecades of happy marriage, a married
OL,14,Flife he valued but of late, the
OL,15,Fdifficulties experienced as a result
OL,16,Fof Carol's medical condition and
OL,17,Findeed his own mental health, led to
OL,18,Fthe unfortunate event.
