OL,6,F"He was and remains tired of life and
OL,7,Fthat in itself is perhaps a
OL,8,Fdemonstration of the very real stress
OL,9,Fand pain that he himself was enduring."
OL,11,FJailing Matthews, Judge Kristina
OL,12,FMontgomery KC said he killed his wife
OL,13,Fbecause he "could not bear witness to
OL,14,Fher suffering", but said Mrs Matthews
OL,15,Fwanted to live.
