OL,6,FShe said: "You were both her husband
OL,7,Fand her carer and all of those who
OL,8,Fhave spoken about your relationship
OL,9,Fdescribe it as your being devoted to
OL,10,Fher, your being a loving husband and
OL,11,Fthat you doted on her.
OL,13,F"This was plainly a very challenging
OL,14,Fperiod in your lives but she still saw
OL,15,Fthe quality in her life and wanted it
OL,16,Fto continue."
OL,18,FHe was given a 10-year minimum
OL,19,Fsentence, reduced to nine years and
OL,20,F228 days due to time already served on
OL,21,Fremand.
